Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Carmelo Anthony?

Carmelo Anthony is 41 years old.

Where was Carmelo Anthony born?

Carmelo Anthony was born in Brooklyn, New York.

When was Carmelo Anthony born?

Carmelo Anthony was born on May 29, 1984.

How tall is Carmelo Anthony?

Carmelo Anthony is 6-7 (201 cm) tall.

How much did Carmelo Anthony weigh when playing?

Carmelo Anthony weighed 238 lbs (107 kg) when playing.

Is Carmelo Anthony in the Hall of Fame?

Carmelo Anthony was inducted to the Hall of Fame as a Player in 2025 (Full List) .

When was Carmelo Anthony drafted?

Carmelo Anthony was drafted by Denver Nuggets, 1st round (3rd pick, 3rd overall), 2003 NBA Draft.

What position did Carmelo Anthony play?

Small Forward and Power Forward.

When did Carmelo Anthony retire?

Carmelo Anthony last played in 2022.

What is Carmelo Anthony's net worth?

Carmelo Anthony made at least $266,350,839 playing professional basketball.

How much did Carmelo Anthony make?

Carmelo Anthony made $26,243,760 in 2018.

What did Carmelo Anthony average?

Carmelo Anthony averaged 22.5 points, 6.2 rebounds, and 2.7 assists per game.

How many rings does Carmelo Anthony have?

Carmelo Anthony won 0 championships.

What is Carmelo Anthony's Instagram account?

Carmelo Anthony is on Instagram at carmeloanthony.

What schools did Carmelo Anthony attend?

Carmelo Anthony attended Towson Catholic in Towson, Maryland, Oak Hill Academy in Mouth of Wilson, Virginia and Syracuse.
